{"tid":1605560,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家係咪唔記得咩叫兄弟爬山？","createTime":"2019-09-30T10:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:17:23.000Z","uid":88551,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7623d370b35fa42529cef5384bb0eb6d684f63","tid":1605560,"uid":88551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:18:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲嘈乜撚野集合定分區？<br />\n我地最多就係和理非<br />\n和理非要靚要震撼咪去港島聚人遊行<br />\n分散狗力又得 打卡靚靚又得<br />\n勇武各區各自打狗 遊擊閃電戰又得<br />\n總之全世界人一齊出黎賀佢老母！<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分化不割蓆我地先有機會贏架！<br />\n黎個運動冇大台架 洗乜有共識？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十月一號 賀佢老母</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同意幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"c58a14ee732f0babef3d2df2d1a359b8c78c938c","tid":1605560,"uid":88551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"c026818704b8e9f063c3d7498b8d866177d2a922","tid":1605560,"uid":229886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"尋晚，你老婆陪我瞓覺，<br />\n瞓到唔願起身，<br />\n仲話留我喺度食飯，<br />\n葱、菜、牛肉，剁爛，<br />\n分開煮多兩餐，<br />\n橫掂有餸落定生抽，<br />\n煮三斤羊扒，<br />\n食哪，食喇，食啦！<br />\n成日冇著衫褲，<br />\n你老婆光脫脫打掃，豪放，<br />\n你老婆招呼好周到，<br />\n人見，人愛，朋友愛！"},{"pid":"14fc667f0b338d22730cb7b90809cbb89c0f0f99","tid":1605560,"uid":88551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c0464176ebf061aa920bf26a94b7b6f42065fe4c","tid":1605560,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01788e065da9b6e5ffd70119a78332b56bf57163","t